{"tid":971833,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"毒撚係一種態度，一種精神，一種意象","createTime":"2019-01-07T03:08:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-07T08:56:35.000Z","uid":8307,"like":18,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2d9c912a0a67977b122dd628e063ee6f8173d2a8","tid":971833,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T03:08:16.000Z","msg":"毒撚係一種態度，一種精神，一種意象<br />\n佢並唔代表電腦前面個會員既真實狀況<br />\n<br />\n我地戴上「毒撚」呢種面具<br />\n令大家對我地既預設形象就係樣衰弱智既人<br />\n<br />\n也因如此，當每個人都係毒撚<br />\n可以顯露個人價值既就只有單純既話語同行為<br />\n<br />\n冇外在美醜，冇刻板印象，冇地位高低<br />\n只有最純粹既思考價值<br />\n<br />\nThis is 毒撚<br />\n<br />\n我再強調一次<br />\n毒撚就是毒撚，偽毒唔好叫自己毒撚<br />\n<br />\n我地毒撚好不容易建立起自己既文化圈<br />\n結果你地呢班外來既偽毒為左想融入我地都開始自稱毒撚<br />\n咁樣係對毒撚既侮辱<br />\n就好像facebook一堆閪人生勝利組都鍾意自稱自己好撚毒一樣<br />\n你老母閪根本係到嘲笑人<br />\n明唔明啊!"},{"pid":"050f8418f5822e3b26a139889022f092e28bce7f","tid":971833,"uid":2223,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T03:49:11.000Z","msg":"我毒我自豪！"},{"pid":"b2507604d22c3a955281831153331277b082829b","tid":971833,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"050f8418f5822e3b26a139889022f092e28bce7f","tid":971833,"uid":2223,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T03:49:11.000Z","msg":"我毒我自豪！"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T04:05:59.000Z","msg":"Ching ho ball"},{"pid":"1f1817c54590d53cbafb5bc11ec4c895c742831c","tid":971833,"uid":2223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b2507604d22c3a955281831153331277b082829b","tid":971833,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"050f8418f5822e3b26a139889022f092e28bce7f","tid":971833,"uid":2223,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T03:49:11.000Z","msg":"我毒我自豪！"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T04:05:59.000Z","msg":"Ching ho ball"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T04:12:24.000Z","msg":"好耐無聽過咁意氣昂揚嘅演說<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a436751e17acc18fe82de8ff978f5136a2682e7","tid":971833,"ui